+20: UART7
+21: KEYPAD
+22: TIMER0
+23: TIMER1
+24: TIMER2
+25: TIMER3
+26: CAN
+27: DMA
+28: PIO
+29: TOUCH_PANEL
+30: AUDIO_CODEC
+31: LRADC
+32: SDMC0
